    <section class="lead-for-good">
        <div class="hero-banner">
            <h1 class="lead-for-good-title" property="name">Lead for Good</h1>
            <img src="https://grgivecamp.org/assets/lead-for-good.jpg" alt="LFG | Lead for Good" />
        </div>
        <div class="register-block">
            <a class="link-button accent-button" href="https://www.eventbrite.com/e/lead-for-good-building-a-cohesive-team-registration-59867876430?ref=ebtnebregn" target="_blank">Register Now</a>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="content">

        <div class="what-is-code-for-good">
            <div class="wrapper">
                <div class="text-block">
                    <h2>What is Code for Good?</h2>
                    <p>
                        We’re a volunteer-run collective of technology professionals in Grand Rapids, Michigan, dedicated to creating tech solutions for non-profit agencies.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Our primary event is <strong>Weekend for Good</strong> in November, but we are involved with projects all year long.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Want to help? <a asp-page="./Volunteer">Let us know!</a>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="button-block">
                    <div class="heart-stack">
                        <div class="call-out-text-over-heart">Can you help my non-profit?</div>
                    </div>
                    <a class="button" asp-page="./NonprofitAgencies">Apply</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="working-together">
            <img src="~/assets/working-together.jpg" alt="Working Together"/>
        </div>
        <div class="what-is-weekend-for-good">
            <div class="wrapper">
                <div class="button-block">
                    <div class="heart-stack">
                        <div class="call-out-text-over-heart">I want to donate my time!</div>
                    </div>
                    <a class="button" asp-page="./Volunteer">Volunteer</a>
                </div>
                <div class="text-block">
                    <h2>Ok, What's Weekend for Good?</h2>
                    <p>Weekend for Good is an event held in collaboration with <a href="https://westmichigan.aiga.org/">AIGA West Michigan</a>.</p>
                    <p> On <strong>@Model.WeekendForGoodDateRange</strong>, volunteers who are experts in software development, design and other fields donate their time to non-profits, creating custom software to further their charitable missions.</p>
                    <p>In turn, those non-profits create meaningful change here in Grand Rapids and around the globe.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>